Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleigh Beggies are valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:34.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夜の愛し仔(スレイ･ベガ)は貴重ですから
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.46,0:02:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones with potential and\Nambition are treasures, aren't they?
