Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰って！
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you like it?
