Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.03,0:03:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You both look terrible.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.07,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you come in here more quietly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（レンフレッド）\Nもっと静かに入ってこい
