Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:27.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不老不死は永遠のテーマさ
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pathetic dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くだらん夢だ
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stuck-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,潔癖だなあ
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant, but you'll make enemies being like that.
