Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（レンフレッド）\N味方なんぞ 数人いれば 十分だろう
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need more than a few people on my side.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, anyway...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.23,0:03:39.53,Alt,,0,0,0,,Tory, that's too much!
